  "title": "Laboratory Technician | Chemical Materials | Junior Assistant",
  "description": "<p>Our client is a Manufacturing MNC for Chemical Materials. Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a Lab Technician  to be part of their Laboratory Team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the <strong>West - easily accessible.</strong></p><p><strong>Duties of Lab Technician :</strong></p><ul><li>Measure and weigh paint base materials according to prescribed formulas.</li><li>Mix and tint paints with colorants, ensuring precise formulation.</li><li>Operate shaking equipment to achieve uniform paint samples.</li><li>Prepare drawdowns for visual inspection and spectrophotometric analysis.</li><li>Label, organize, and prepare paint samples for submission.</li><li>Maintain a clean and safe laboratory environment in compliance with standards.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Nitec or or equivalent.</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><ul><li><strong>Email Address: </strong><a href=\"mailto:jobs@recruitpedia.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></a></li><li>EA License No: 19C9682</li><li>EA Personnel No: R2198636 (Oh Puey Xin)</li></ul>",
